content:
Caro Lotan I think works with Pickman/Thais/Helot, probably more Pickman than Thais if you want to throw Aigis in there
Ultra Lotan can work with Horla and Clementine, and I'd do a second keyflare character because fuck it why not; 
Aequor Lotan is probably going to be a bit like Aurita in that it's ~~bad~~ reliant on red stance tentacle waves. You might also want something like Dreams covenant or dimensional image for this one so you can get a bunch of copies of Blade of Defiance.
